    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This white paper discusses accounting requirements for IPng.  It recommends that all IPng packets carry accounting tags, which would vary in size.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
